{%- comment -%}
  Productdetailpagina (Online Store 2.0).
  Reproduceert exact de blauwdruk product.html: tweekoloms galerij + sticky info,
  varianten, accordions, maat-adviseur en "Combineer met".

  De pagina-eigen CSS staat — net als in de blauwdruk — in een {% style %}-blok
  (base.css mag niet gewijzigd worden). De maat-adviseur-JS staat onderaan inline,
  precies zoals in de blauwdruk; de generieke hooks komen uit global.js.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- style -%}
  .product {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: start;
    padding-block: var(--sp-2) var(--section-y);
  }
  .product-gallery__main { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  .product-gallery__main.media { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  .product-gallery__main img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  .product-gallery__thumbs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--sp-0_75);
    margin-top: var(--sp-0_75);
  }
  .product-gallery__thumb {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color var(--t-fast);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .product-gallery__thumb .media { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  .product-gallery__thumb img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  .product-gallery__thumb.is-active { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .product-gallery__thumb:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

  .product-info { position: sticky; top: calc(76px + var(--sp-1_5)); }
  .product-info__eyebrow { margin-bottom: var(--sp-0_75); }
  .product-info__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.85rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-0_75);
  }
  .product-info__price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-1);
  }
  .product-info__desc {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-1_5);
  }
  .product-info hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: var(--border);
    margin-block: var(--sp-1_5);
  }
  .option-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-0_75);
  }
  .option-label .option-value {
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: none;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .option-block { margin-bottom: var(--sp-1_5); }
  .sizefinder-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .sizefinder-icon {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    flex: none;
    transform-origin: center;
    animation: sizefinder-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .sizefinder-link:hover .sizefinder-icon { animation: none; transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1.12); }
  @keyframes sizefinder-pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.18) rotate(-6deg); }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .sizefinder-icon { animation: none; }
  }
  .swatches { display: flex; gap: var(--sp-0_75); }
  .swatch {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    padding: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    position: relative;
    transition: box-shadow var(--t-fast);
  }
  .swatch span {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 3px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(28, 26, 23, 0.08);
  }
  .swatch.is-selected {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--bg), 0 0 0 2px var(--ink);
  }
  /* Witte swatches krijgen een dunne rand zodat ze zichtbaar blijven */
  .swatch.swatch--light { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .swatch.swatch--light span { border-color: rgba(28, 26, 23, 0.25); }
  .swatch[disabled],
  .size-btn[disabled] {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }
  .swatch[disabled] { text-decoration: none; }
  .size-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--sp-0_5); }
  .size-btn {
    min-width: 48px;
    padding: 0.6em 0.9em;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--surface);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: border-color var(--t-fast), background var(--t-fast), color var(--t-fast);
  }
  .size-btn:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .size-btn.is-selected {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }
  .qty {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  .qty button {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: color var(--t-fast);
  }
  .qty button:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .qty input {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    text-align: center;
    border: none;
    border-inline: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: transparent;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    -moz-appearance: textfield;
  }
  .qty input::-webkit-outer-spin-button,
  .qty input::-webkit-inner-spin-button { -webkit-appearance: none; margin: 0; }
  .product-form__select-wrap { margin-bottom: var(--sp-1); }
  .product-form__select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.7em 0.9em;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--surface);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .product-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-0_75);
    align-items: stretch;
    margin-block: var(--sp-1_5) var(--sp-0_75);
  }
  .product-actions .btn[type="submit"] { flex: 1; }
  /* "Nu kopen": volle breedte onder de actie-rij */
  .product-form .btn--block {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-1_5);
  }
  /* VERLANGLIJST = klein, rond hart-icoon-knopje naast "In winkelmand" */
  .wishlist-heart {
    flex: none;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    align-self: stretch;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color var(--t-fast), color var(--t-fast), transform var(--t-fast);
  }
  .wishlist-heart svg { display: block; transition: fill var(--t-fast); }
  .wishlist-heart:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: scale(1.06);
  }
  .wishlist-heart.is-active {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .wishlist-heart.is-active svg { fill: currentColor; }
  .product-usps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .product-usps li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem; }
  .product-usps svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; color: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .product-accordions { margin-top: var(--sp-1_5); }
  .accordion { border-top: var(--border); }
  .accordion:last-of-type { border-bottom: var(--border); }
  .accordion > summary {
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
    padding-block: var(--sp-1);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .accordion > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .accordion > summary::after {
    content: "+";
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: transform var(--t-fast);
  }
  .accordion[open] > summary::after { content: "–"; }
  .accordion__body {
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-1);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  .accordion__body p + p { margin-top: var(--sp-0_75); }
  .accordion__body ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .accordion__body li { padding-left: 1.1rem; position: relative; }
  .accordion__body li::before {
    content: "·";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  /* Productdetails als open secties (geen dropdown) */
  .product-details { margin-top: var(--sp-1); }
  .product-detail {
    border-top: var(--border);
    padding-top: var(--sp-1_5);
    margin-top: var(--sp-1_5);
  }
  .product-detail:first-child { margin-top: var(--sp-1); }
  .product-detail__title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-0_75);
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .product { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-2); }
    .product-info { position: static; top: auto; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .product-actions { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .product-actions .qty { align-self: stretch; }
    .product-actions .btn[type="submit"] { flex: 1 1 auto; }
  }
  .sizefinder[hidden] { display: none; }
  .sizefinder {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  .sizefinder__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(28, 26, 23, 0.45);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
  }
  .sizefinder__dialog {
    position: relative;
    width: min(460px, 100%);
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -30px rgba(28, 26, 23, 0.4);
    animation: sf-pop 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  @keyframes sf-pop {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .sizefinder__dialog { animation: none; } }
  .sizefinder__close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.6rem;
    right: 0.85rem;
    width: 2.25rem;
    height: 2.25rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--muted);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .sizefinder__close:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .sizefinder__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.65rem; margin: 0.2rem 0 0.5rem; }
  .sizefinder__intro { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .sizefinder__form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .sizefinder__submit { margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .sizefinder__row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  @media (max-width: 400px) { .sizefinder__row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .sizefinder .field input,
  .sizefinder .field select { font-size: 1rem; }
  .sizefinder__result:focus { outline: none; }
  .sizefinder__edit {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .sizefinder__edit:hover { color: var(--accent-deep); }
  .sizefinder__error { color: var(--sale); font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .sizefinder__result {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .sizefinder__result-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .sizefinder__size {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0.3rem 0 0.55rem;
  }
  .sizefinder__explain { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .sizefinder__disclaimer { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.85rem; }
  .sizefinder__table { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .sizefinder__table summary { cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent); }
  .sizefinder__table table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
  .sizefinder__table th,
  .sizefinder__table td {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-align: left;
  }
  .sizefinder__table th {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* Dunnere, zachtere omlijning om de beoordelingen-kaarten (minder zwaar) */
  .product-reviews .review,
  .product-reviews .review-summary { border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 45%, transparent); }

  /* Verdeling van de beoordelingen voor dit product (demo-data) */
  .review-summary__bars .review-bar:nth-child(1) .review-bar__fill { width: 83%; }
  .review-summary__bars .review-bar:nth-child(2) .review-bar__fill { width: 14%; }
  .review-summary__bars .review-bar:nth-child(3) .review-bar__fill { width: 3%; }
  .review-summary__bars .review-bar:nth-child(4) .review-bar__fill { width: 0; }
  .review-summary__bars .review-bar:nth-child(5) .review-bar__fill { width: 0; }
  /* Sticky 'In winkelmand'-balk (verschijnt bij scrollen voorbij de knop) */
  .sticky-atc {
    position: fixed;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 90;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: 0 -6px 24px rgba(28, 26, 23, 0.08);
    padding: 0.7rem 0;
    transform: translateY(105%);
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: transform var(--t-fast), visibility var(--t-fast);
  }
  .sticky-atc.is-visible {
    transform: translateY(0);
    visibility: visible;
  }
  .sticky-atc__inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
  }
  .sticky-atc__info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .sticky-atc__thumb {
    width: 44px;
    height: 56px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .sticky-atc__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .sticky-atc__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  .sticky-atc__price {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .sticky-atc__btn {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .sticky-atc__thumb { display: none; }
    .sticky-atc__name { font-size: 0.92rem; max-width: 48vw; }
    .sticky-atc__price { font-size: 0.82rem; }
    .sticky-atc__btn { padding-left: 1.2em; padding-right: 1.2em; }
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

{%- liquid
  assign current_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
  assign eyebrow_text = ''
  if section.settings.show_vendor and product.vendor != blank
    assign eyebrow_text = shop.name | append: ' · ' | append: product.vendor
  elsif product.type != blank
    assign eyebrow_text = shop.name | append: ' · ' | append: product.type
  else
    assign eyebrow_text = shop.name
  endif
-%}

<!-- BREADCRUMB -->
<nav class="container container--wide breadcrumb" aria-label="Kruimelpad">
  <ul>
    <li><a href="{{ routes.root_url }}">Home</a></li>
    {%- if collection.url != blank -%}
      <li><a href="{{ collection.url }}">{{ collection.title }}</a></li>
    {%- else -%}
      <li><a href="{{ routes.all_products_collection_url }}">Collectie</a></li>
    {%- endif -%}
    <li><span aria-current="page">{{ product.title }}</span></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- PRODUCTDETAIL: tweekoloms (galerij + info) -->
<section class="container container--wide product">

  <!-- LINKS: productgalerij. Loopt product.media; valt terug op .media-placeholder als er geen media is. -->
  <div class="product-gallery reveal">
    <figure>
      {%- if product.featured_media != blank -%}
        <div class="product-gallery__main" data-gallery-main>
          {{ product.featured_media | image_url: width: 1000 | image_tag: loading: 'eager', fetchpriority: 'high', widths: '400, 600, 800, 1000, 1200', sizes: '(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw', alt: product.featured_media.alt | default: product.title, class: 'product-gallery__main-img' }}
        </div>
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="media product-gallery__main" data-gallery-main data-label="{{ product.title | escape }}"
             role="img" aria-label="{{ product.title | escape }}"></div>
      {%- endif -%}
      <figcaption class="visually-hidden">{{ product.title }}</figcaption>
    </figure>

    {%- if product.media.size > 1 -%}
      <div class="product-gallery__thumbs">
        {%- for media in product.media -%}
          <button class="product-gallery__thumb{% if forloop.first %} is-active{% endif %}" data-gallery-thumb
                  data-media-id="{{ media.id }}"
                  data-full="{{ media | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                  aria-label="Toon afbeelding {{ forloop.index }}">
            {{ media | image_url: width: 300 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', alt: media.alt | default: product.title, widths: '150, 200, 300', sizes: '(max-width: 900px) 22vw, 11vw' }}
          </button>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    {%- elsif product.media.size == 0 -%}
      {%- comment -%} Fallback-thumbs in de stijl van de blauwdruk wanneer er nog geen foto's zijn {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="product-gallery__thumbs">
        <button class="product-gallery__thumb is-active" data-gallery-thumb
                data-label="{{ product.title | escape }} · vooraanzicht" aria-label="Toon vooraanzicht">
          <div class="media" data-label="Voor"></div>
        </button>
        <button class="product-gallery__thumb" data-gallery-thumb
                data-label="{{ product.title | escape }} · achteraanzicht" aria-label="Toon achteraanzicht">
          <div class="media" data-label="Achter"></div>
        </button>
        <button class="product-gallery__thumb" data-gallery-thumb
                data-label="{{ product.title | escape }} · detail" aria-label="Toon detail">
          <div class="media" data-label="Detail"></div>
        </button>
        <button class="product-gallery__thumb" data-gallery-thumb
                data-label="{{ product.title | escape }} · gedragen" aria-label="Toon gedragen">
          <div class="media" data-label="Gedragen"></div>
        </button>
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <!-- RECHTS: productinfo (sticky op desktop) -->
  <div class="product-info reveal" data-delay="1">
    <p class="eyebrow product-info__eyebrow">{{ eyebrow_text }}</p>
    <h1 class="product-info__title">{{ product.title }}</h1>
    <p class="product-info__price">
      <span data-product-price>{{ current_variant.price | money }}</span>
      {%- if current_variant.compare_at_price > current_variant.price -%}
        <span class="price-sale"><s>{{ current_variant.compare_at_price | money }}</s></span>
      {%- endif -%}
    </p>
    {%- if product.description != blank -%}
      <div class="product-info__desc rte">{{ product.description | strip_html | truncatewords: 55 }}</div>
    {%- endif -%}

    <hr />

    {%- comment -%}
      Visuele varianten in de stijl van de blauwdruk (swatches/maat-knoppen).
      Elke knop draagt data-opt-position (1/2) en data-opt-value, zodat de inline
      JS de juiste variant kan bepalen en het verborgen veld name="id" kan zetten.
      Kleur-swatches gebruiken de echte Shopify-kleur (swatch.color/.image) met
      terugval op een NL naam->kleur-map.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- for option in product.options_with_values -%}
      {%- assign opt_name_down = option.name | downcase -%}
      {%- if opt_name_down contains 'kleur' or opt_name_down contains 'color' -%}
        <div class="option-block" data-option-block data-opt-position="{{ forloop.index }}">
          <div class="option-label">
            <span>{{ option.name }}</span>
            <span class="option-value" data-color-value>{{ option.selected_value }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatches">
            {%- for value in option.values -%}
              {%- comment -%} Naam betrouwbaar ophalen (werkt voor strings én option-value-objecten) {%- endcomment -%}
              {%- capture v_name -%}{{ value }}{%- endcapture -%}{%- assign v_name = v_name | strip -%}
              {%- comment -%} Selectie betrouwbaar bepalen via string-vergelijking of value.selected {%- endcomment -%}
              {%- capture sel_name -%}{{ option.selected_value }}{%- endcapture -%}{%- assign sel_name = sel_name | strip -%}
              {%- assign is_sel = false -%}
              {%- if value.selected -%}{%- assign is_sel = true -%}{%- elsif v_name == sel_name -%}{%- assign is_sel = true -%}{%- endif -%}
              {%- comment -%} Kleur/afbeelding bepalen volgens contract-volgorde {%- endcomment -%}
              {%- assign swatch_color = '' -%}
              {%- assign swatch_image = '' -%}
              {%- if value.swatch.color -%}
                {%- assign swatch_color = value.swatch.color -%}
              {%- elsif value.swatch.image -%}
                {%- assign swatch_image = value.swatch.image | image_url: width: 80 -%}
              {%- else -%}
                {%- capture v_hex -%}{%- render 'sm-color-hex', name: v_name -%}{%- endcapture -%}{%- assign v_hex = v_hex | strip -%}
                {%- if v_hex != blank -%}{%- assign swatch_color = v_hex -%}{%- endif -%}
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- comment -%} (Bijna-)witte kleuren krijgen swatch--light voor zichtbaarheid {%- endcomment -%}
              {%- assign is_light = false -%}
              {%- if swatch_color != blank -%}
                {%- assign sc_down = swatch_color | downcase -%}
                {%- if sc_down == '#ffffff' or sc_down == '#fff' or sc_down == '#f3efe7' -%}{%- assign is_light = true -%}{%- endif -%}
              {%- endif -%}
              <button class="swatch{% if is_sel %} is-selected{% endif %}{% if is_light %} swatch--light{% endif %}" type="button"
                      data-opt-button data-opt-position="{{ forloop.parentloop.index }}" data-opt-value="{{ v_name | escape }}"
                      aria-pressed="{% if is_sel %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}"
                      aria-label="{{ option.name }} {{ v_name }}"
                      {%- if swatch_image != blank %} style="background-image:url({{ swatch_image }});background-size:cover;"{% elsif swatch_color != blank %} style="background:{{ swatch_color }};"{% else %} style="background:var(--bg-alt);"{% endif %}><span></span></button>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="option-block" data-option-block data-opt-position="{{ forloop.index }}">
          <div class="option-label">
            <span>{{ option.name }}</span>
            {%- if opt_name_down contains 'maat' or opt_name_down contains 'size' -%}
              <a class="link-accent sizefinder-link" href="#maatadvies" data-sizefinder-open>
                <svg class="sizefinder-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
                  <rect x="2" y="8" width="20" height="8" rx="1" />
                  <path d="M6 8v3.5M10 8v4.5M14 8v3.5M18 8v4.5" />
                </svg>
                Maat-adviseur
              </a>
            {%- else -%}
              <span class="option-value">{{ option.selected_value }}</span>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
          <div class="size-grid"{% if opt_name_down contains 'maat' or opt_name_down contains 'size' %} data-size-grid{% endif %}>
            {%- for value in option.values -%}
              <button class="size-btn{% if value == option.selected_value %} is-selected{% endif %}" type="button"
                      data-opt-button data-opt-position="{{ forloop.parentloop.index }}" data-opt-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                      aria-pressed="{% if value == option.selected_value %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}">{{ value }}</button>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}

    <!-- WERKEND PRODUCTFORMULIER: variant-select + aantal + in winkelmand -->
    {%- form 'product', product, id: 'product-form', class: 'product-form' -%}
      {%- comment -%} De variant wordt via de kleur-/maat-knoppen bepaald; geen zichtbare dropdown meer. {%- endcomment -%}
      <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}" data-variant-id>
      <script type="application/json" data-variant-json>{{ product.variants | json }}</script>

      <div class="product-actions">
        <div class="qty" data-qty>
          <button type="button" data-qty-minus aria-label="Aantal verlagen">−</button>
          <label class="visually-hidden" for="qty-input">Aantal</label>
          <input id="qty-input" name="quantity" type="number" inputmode="numeric" value="1" min="1" />
          <button type="button" data-qty-plus aria-label="Aantal verhogen">+</button>
        </div>
        <button class="btn" type="submit" name="add" {% unless current_variant.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>
          {%- if current_variant.available -%}In winkelmand{%- else -%}Uitverkocht{%- endif -%}
        </button>
        <!-- VERLANGLIJST = alleen een hart-icoon (UI-only, geen add-to-cart) -->
        <button class="wishlist-heart" type="button" data-wishlist data-name="{{ product.title | escape }}" data-image="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 200 }}" data-url="{{ product.url }}" aria-label="Voeg toe aan verlanglijst">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 20s-7-4.3-9.2-8.4C1.3 8.7 2.7 5.5 5.8 5.1 7.6 4.9 9.2 5.9 12 8c2.8-2.1 4.4-3.1 6.2-2.9 3.1.4 4.5 3.6 3 6.5C19 15.7 12 20 12 20z"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- NU KOPEN: direct naar de kassa (global.js handelt af) -->
      <button class="btn btn--outline btn--block" type="button" data-buy-now {% unless current_variant.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>Nu kopen</button>
    {%- endform -%}

    <!-- USP-regeltjes -->
    <ul class="product-usps">
      <li>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 7h11v8H3z"/><path d="M14 10h4l3 3v2h-7z"/><circle cx="7" cy="17" r="2"/><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="2"/></svg>
        Verzekerde verzending met Track &amp; Trace
      </li>
      <li>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 1 3 6.7"/><path d="M3 19v-4h4"/></svg>
        30 dagen retour, gratis en eenvoudig
      </li>
      <li>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
        Voor 22:00 besteld, morgen in huis
      </li>
    </ul>

    <!-- PRODUCTDETAILS als dropdowns (accordion) -->
    <div class="product-details">
      <details class="accordion" open>
        <summary>Omschrijving</summary>
        <div class="accordion__body rte">
          {%- if product.description != blank -%}
            {{ product.description }}
          {%- else -%}
            <p>Een tijdloos stuk uit de Up to Date Damesmode-collectie, met zorg geselecteerd en gemaakt om lang mee te gaan.</p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="accordion">
        <summary>Materiaal &amp; onderhoud</summary>
        <div class="accordion__body rte">
          {%- if product.metafields.custom.materiaal != blank -%}
            {{ product.metafields.custom.materiaal }}
          {%- else -%}
            <ul>
              <li>Hoogwaardige, ademende materialen</li>
              <li>Zorgvuldig afgewerkte naden</li>
              <li>Gemaakt om lang mee te gaan</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Was op een fijn programma op 30°C met een mild wasmiddel. Niet in de droger; hang op een
            vormvaste hanger en strijk indien gewenst op lage temperatuur.</p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="accordion">
        <summary>Verzending &amp; retour</summary>
        <div class="accordion__body rte">
          {%- if product.metafields.custom.verzending != blank -%}
            {{ product.metafields.custom.verzending }}
          {%- else -%}
            <p>Wij verzenden verzekerd en met Track &amp; Trace: €6,95 binnen Nederland en €9,95 naar
            België. Voor 22:00 besteld op werkdagen betekent morgen in huis.</p>
            <p>Niet helemaal naar wens? Je hebt 30 dagen bedenktijd. Retourneren is gratis en
            eenvoudig met het meegeleverde retourlabel — we storten je aankoopbedrag binnen vijf
            werkdagen terug.</p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="accordion" id="maatadvies">
        <summary>Maatadvies</summary>
        <div class="accordion__body rte">
          {%- if product.metafields.custom.maatadvies != blank -%}
            {{ product.metafields.custom.maatadvies }}
          {%- else -%}
            <p>Twijfel je tussen twee maten? Kies dan de kleinste voor een nettere pasvorm, of de
            grootste als je het kledingstuk graag losser draagt.</p>
            <p>Persoonlijk maatadvies nodig?
            <a class="link-accent" href="{{ pages.contact.url | default: '/pages/contact' }}">Onze stylisten helpen je graag.</a></p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

